{
  "stem": "449.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What she did, she-- she learned photography on stone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for the Italian people, that was something-- in-- in-- in New York, it was something you-- photography on the gravestone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is great.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She became rich.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She became rich.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when she visited us after the first war in 1918, she visited us, and she said, when you are through with your education, you come to me, and you have a job in-- in-- no, she didn't even say after the education.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She wanted to have me right away, working in her shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I made the preparations to-- to get a visa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] oh, I get mixed up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I believe I was already-- I was already an engineer at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When she--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--no, never-- never mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came in 1920, maybe, and said, come and-- come to America.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted always to go to America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when I was 16 years old, [LAUGHS] go back-- 6 years old, my history teacher in the gymnasium, he talked about the Bill of Rights.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "An-- an Austrian teacher talks about the American Bill of Rights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was 16 years old, and I was always very-- I wanted to get rid of the monarchy, and I was a Republican.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wanted-- that was the ideal for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that's my-- that's the country I would like to live-- where they have a Bill of Rights.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I made-- applied for an American visa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to the consul-- and that was in-- in-- I applied in November.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in October, the parliament, the Congress made a law-- a quota law.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- I had to wait seven years for a visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
